    "The Hilbert transform was employed in this study to improve the emotional recognition performance in the arousal and valence model.",
    "Table 12 summarizes the various eye-tracking methods for emotion recognition that we have reviewed in this section.",
    "Metrics in Emotion Recognition ApproachesAs depicted inTable 10, 11, and 12, Emotion recognition, a pivotal aspect of human robot interaction, employs a spectrum of metrics across various methodologies to gauge accuracy and effectiveness.",
